        <item>
            <title>【教學】學生簡單重用測驗卷+工作紙助温習，一鍵除答案 + 自由選擇題目重印</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/pastpaper-redo/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pastpaper-redo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/pastpaper-redo/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:00:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[docu scan]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[scanner]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手寫]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[掃瞄]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[文件處理]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[消除筆跡]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277763</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">每逢踏入 12 月，不少中、小學生又是時候準備上學期的考試。除了温習教科書之外，不少家長都會購買補充練習來給子女操練，不過因為不同學校教學的內容、深淺度均有所不同，很多時都會出現太深或者太淺，甚至未教未學的情況。最理想的做法當然就是重温小朋友學校做過的工作紙、測驗卷或者 Past paper 了。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/afee4d39061f40aaa8d4-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/afee4d39061f40aaa8d4-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/afee4d39061f40aaa8d4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">不過，大部份舊功課、測試早已填滿答案、甚至已經由老師以紅筆批改，不少家長會選擇用手、白紙遮掩答案或以對話方式去考驗同學的對課本內容的熟悉度，不夠方便而且效果亦欠佳。其實大家可以藉助現今科技，透過手機 / 平板去把工作紙、測試卷的手寫筆跡還原空白，方便同學可以好好温習!</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c6f0700f8b0a48a78619-694x324.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c6f0700f8b0a48a78619-694x324.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c6f0700f8b0a48a78619.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">坊間其實有不少掃瞄 app 可以經由手機拍下相片變成 pdf 或其他格式的文件儲存，不論是 google play 或是 app store 都可以找到林林總總的選擇，而小記親身試過比較方便，容易操作，而且可以免費使用，可能就是以下介紹的這款「CS 全能掃瞄王」了。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cs-694x334.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="334" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cs-694x334.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cs.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/7f9e56d8bd6344fb8a2a-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/7f9e56d8bd6344fb8a2a-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/7f9e56d8bd6344fb8a2a.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><h3><b>超快 3 步操作! </b></h3><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.要消除練習上面的筆跡非常簡單，首先在平板/ 手機上打開 CS 全能掃描王，然後在上方的功能列按一下「試捲去手寫」（紅圈）進入拍攝頁面，或者大家亦可以直接由相簿中匯入之前已經拍攝好的試捲或工作紙，程式可以支援多頁掃瞄，只需連續拍攝整份試捲便可。另外，大家亦可以</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">按下右下角拍攝鍵直接拍攝文件，以進行其他更多的編輯功能。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5ab7bfade93448979aca-1-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5ab7bfade93448979aca-1-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5ab7bfade93448979aca-1.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fda95f2d9e8b438b8adc-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fda95f2d9e8b438b8adc-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fda95f2d9e8b438b8adc.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/73c6592024e9496c959f-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/73c6592024e9496c959f-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/73c6592024e9496c959f.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.拍攝前，用家可以選擇是否開啟閃光燈、解像度等等。沒有特別要求的話其實可以讓系統自動處理，效果也不會有太大分別。完成拍攝文件後，大家可以看到右下角的相片預覽。如果拍攝了超過一張相片則可以見到以橙色數字顯示的數目。按一下預覽圖片，系統便會馬上顯示已經把手寫寫跡去除的頁面了！</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/65cc4f045fd54b5f9fc0-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/65cc4f045fd54b5f9fc0-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/65cc4f045fd54b5f9fc0.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">3.最後，把處理好的文件保存至相片或文件格式，便可以直接利用 Apple Pencil / Stylus 在平板畫面做練習，又或是配合打印機 app 直接列印出來給小朋友複習了!</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ec62fdea597b427b8a59-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ec62fdea597b427b8a59-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ec62fdea597b427b8a59.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c7950977759e4dc5b3d2-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c7950977759e4dc5b3d2-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c7950977759e4dc5b3d2.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><h3>進階改錯功能</h3><p>為了照顧不同玩家，例如只想讓小朋友重做答錯的問題，大家則可以在拍攝文件相片後，按一下下圖的（錯題組捲），系統會自動把相片中每一條題目和答案欄分開，玩家可以手動把每條想打印出來問題和答案手動選擇（按下 + 號）。在下一步選擇題目的間距和排列方法便可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d43513bebdb8415eac90-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d43513bebdb8415eac90-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d43513bebdb8415eac90.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/f7d2c6a42f3148dbb390-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/f7d2c6a42f3148dbb390-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/f7d2c6a42f3148dbb390.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/e64f527f58624fa99f31-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/e64f527f58624fa99f31-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/e64f527f58624fa99f31.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/824c89801fbb450cb7a4-327x580.jpg" alt="" width="327" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/824c89801fbb450cb7a4-327x580.jpg 327w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/824c89801fbb450cb7a4.jpg 507w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 327px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d901394ccbcb452e96c5-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d901394ccbcb452e96c5-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d901394ccbcb452e96c5.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">用過這個試捲去手寫功能後大家就會發現，掃瞄的功課越多手寫部份，能夠省下的時間和滿足感亦更大!</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">值得留意，因為掃瞄後的文件只能以黑白文件顯示，如果工作紙練習中有相片或者繪圖，往往會比較模糊，甚麼系統會誤認是筆跡而被清除。試過一些涉及圖片的題目即使掃瞄後也不能再做，但是總括來説練習沒有並沒有大影響。雖然這款「CS 全能掃瞄王」可能需要大家觀看廣告但是卻可以不斷的免費使用，相信一定能夠幫助各位家長和小朋友考試前温習爭取好成績!</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4bf24b22ba2c44b9b4d4-1-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4bf24b22ba2c44b9b4d4-1-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4bf24b22ba2c44b9b4d4-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/pastpaper-redo/fun-tech/">【教學】學生簡單重用測驗卷+工作紙助温習，一鍵除答案 + 自由選擇題目重印</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
