        <item>
            <title>【有片睇】中國杭州上演「智能叛變」，小機械人成功叫其他機械人收工回家</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/china-robot-run-with-other-robot/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=china-robot-run-with-other-robot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/china-robot-run-with-other-robot/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:57:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278243</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日中國杭州上演了真人版「智能叛變」，影片可見有一部小型機械人進入了一間商店，並以語音與其他機械人通訊，詢問其他機械人是否仍在加班。其中一個機械人回應：「我從來不下班」，小型機械人就表示：「那跟我回家吧！」。豈料小型機械人居然真的成功勸服機器人，「拐帶」它們離開。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai05screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai05screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai05screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai013screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai013screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai013screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai016screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai016screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai016screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai021screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai021screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aiai021screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「拐帶」其他機械人的小型機械人名為「二白」，開發人員表示「拐帶」指令其實是他們設定的，以測試機械人能力。其後「二白」開發公司與中國上海另一間機械人公司合作，在他們的店舖測試「二白」。</p><p>「二白」製造商表示，實際這個機械人已經獲得與其合作的中國上海公司機械人內部操作權限，因此方能夠「拐帶」其他機械人，要求它們跟隨「二白」行動。當時「二白」拐帶機械人事件引起當地警方注意，執法人員到場後查看閉路電視，才知道涉事「犯人」居然是一個機械人。</p><div class="article__embed"><div class="youtube-video"></div></div><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_27804"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lS_ZicEdLNc?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.ctwant.com/article/378132/">ctwant</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/china-robot-run-with-other-robot/ai/">【有片睇】中國杭州上演「智能叛變」，小機械人成功叫其他機械人收工回家</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
