        <item>
            <title>【評測】Noble Audio FoKus APOLLO 頭戴式耳機，平板動圈混合單元 + -35dB ANC 降噪</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/noble-audio-fokus-apollo/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=noble-audio-fokus-apollo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/noble-audio-fokus-apollo/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:30:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FoKus APOLLO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Noble Audio]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Noble Audio FoKus APOLLO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平板動圈混合單元]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[真無線藍牙耳機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273005</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美國知名音響品牌 Noble Audio 近日迎來 10 週年紀念，慶祝之際特別推出了 FoKus APOLLO 頭戴式耳機。此款耳機不僅是品牌首度進軍頭戴式耳機市場初試啼聲之作，更是全球首款採用「平板 + 動圈混合單元」的無線頭戴耳機。適逢秋高氣爽的季節，換上耳罩式耳機倍覺適宜。現在就讓小編和大家開箱看看，試試 FoKus APOLLO 表現如何吧。</p><h3></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09791-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09791-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09791.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>包裝精美，收納盒保護度高</h2><p>Noble Audio FoKus APOLLO 的包裝設計非常精美，極具儀式感。包裝盒採用打開式設計，開箱時猶如「拆禮物」般，令用家倍感期待。包裝內附的耳機收納盒設有手抽設計，便於外出攜帶。</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00284-694x462.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00284.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09779-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09779-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09779.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09781-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09781-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09781.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開箱時有如「拆禮物」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09786-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09786-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09786.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲收納盒設有手抽</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09824-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09824-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09824.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可以讓用家帶着周圍去</p><p>值得一讚的是，收納盒採用厚實的蜂巢式結構，保護力十足，能有效抵禦日常碰撞，讓用家無後顧之憂。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273280" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09787-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09787-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09787.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲蜂巢式設計配合特厚咕𠱸</p><h2>配件齊全，靈活應對各種連接需求</h2><p>打開收納盒後即可見説明書、耳機主體、3.5mm AUX 線及 USB-C 充電線，還附有 3.5mm 轉 4.4mm 與 6.3mm 的轉接頭，並附上飛機用航空轉換插頭。FoKus APOLLO 除內置收音咪外，還額外配置了一個可拆卸咪高峯，以滿足對通話質素要求較高的用家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09788-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09788-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09788.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09789-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09789-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09789.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲設有多個轉接頭及可拆卸咪高峯</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
