        <item>
            <title>中國公園驚現機械人放機械狗，網民：看起來很詭異、步姿似急尿</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/robot-and-robot-dog/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=robot-and-robot-dog</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/robot-and-robot-dog/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 11:00:57 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
