            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>人形機械人發展日益蓬勃，近日 X （前稱 Twitter）有網民指在中國的一個公園看見有人形機械人在放狗，仔細一看，那隻也是機械狗。下面有網民回應指，這件事看起來令人毛骨悚然。另外有網民指，不理解為甚麼要用機械人放機械狗。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-media-max-width="560"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">A robot walking its robotic dog in a park in China<a href="https://t.co/gkhfygFY8n">pic.twitter.com/gkhfygFY8n</a></p><p>— Massimo (@Rainmaker1973) <a href="https://twitter.com/Rainmaker1973/status/1862077105611178389?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 28, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
網民 @Rainmaker1973 今日在 X （前稱 Twitter）分享了一條影片，影片可見有一個人形機械人正在放狗，而機械人放的狗也是一隻機械狗。影片引來大批網民回應，有網民表示看起來很詭異，不希望未來機械人放機械狗會成為主流。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">That is super creepy. I don&#8217;t look forward to that becoming mainstream.</p><p>— Roggey (@roggey187) <a href="https://twitter.com/roggey187/status/1862077706004767032?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 28, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>另外有網民笑指機械人走路的姿態像是要去廁所般。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">The walker robot looks like he really needs to find tbe restroom.</p><p>— Colin Sheehan 🐴 (@csheehan45) <a href="https://twitter.com/csheehan45/status/1862108106643140897?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 28, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://x.com/Rainmaker1973/status/1862077105611178389">Rainmaker1973@X</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
